reviewText: I was looking for the movie of Babe Ruth's life
Wow....phenomenal!!! Truly outstanding, and great old film clips  as well
good movie, but for some reason on Amazon's website,the cast and trivia were for  a different move starring william bendix, not the documentary of the Babe's life.
I am a baseball person, love the game. This is a good film for someone who loves the game and the Babe. Lots of pictures and a biography of one of baseball's best.

I was looking for the original Babe Ruth Movie that I remember watching when I was a youngster. The "Babe" with John Goodman is a good movie but not the original. The Babe Ruth Story  above is more of a biography on the player.
